{{Databox|en=Air Tamajeq language}}
'''Ayr Tamajeq''' (Tayiṛt) tga yat tmzarayt n [[Tamacq]] lli igan s yixf-nns yat zzɣ [[tutlayin titwargiyin|tutlayin titwargin]]. Ar si-s sawaln [[itwargin]] lli izdɣn ɣ idrarn n Ayr ɣ [[Tsga n Agadz]] ɣ Nnijr.

[https://www.ethnologue.com/ ''Ethnologue''] ibder snat tntlayin: Ayr (Tayert) d Tanassfarwat (Tamagarast/Tamesgrest). Blench (2006) yanni is gant timzarayin-ad snat tutlayin bḍanin. Ismmu Ingal d Gofat am tntlayin n Ayr/Tayirt d Azerori am tntala n Tamesgrest.

